1
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,020
Your Highness.

2
00:01:58,960 --> 00:01:59,800
You are...

3
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,540
A-Ling.

4
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:03,400
Cousin,

5
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,400
what brings you here?

6
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,199
I happened to steal a pot of fine wine.

7
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,930
Let's sit and chat over a drink.

8
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,440
So, it is the Prince of Qi.

9
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:18,300
No wonder you resemble the Crown Prince.

10
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,960
You really are brothers.

11
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,720
Who are you?

12
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:21,880
I am Xiao Ling.

13
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,960
A-Ling is General Xiao's eldest daughter.

14
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,320
She has always lived in the military camp,

15
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,180
so you wouldn't know her, Cousin.

16
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,800
Thanks to Your Highness,

17
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,680
my father allowed me to return to the camp.

18
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,610
I came to offer a gift in gratitude.

19
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,120
Here.

20
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,280
This is the tooth of a wolf I hunted myself.

21
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,010
It's for you.

22
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:44,970
Thank you, Ling.

23
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,360
Back then, Father forbade me from marrying Li Yunxi,

24
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,360
but I insisted.

25
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,880
Now I've fled the palace in disgrace,

26
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:06,140
and I have to ask him to help save Hanxing.

27
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,730
Fifth Uncle.

28
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,120
Fifth Aunt.

29
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,000
Miss.

30
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,520
Miss.

31
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:27,970
Uncle Zhong,

32
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,760
what is going on?

33
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,700
Where is my father?

34
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,880
Just now, a group of black-clad assassins

35
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,320
rushed in.

36
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:39,760
Miss, you must run!

37
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,360
Run!

38
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,570
Uncle Zhong.

39
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,560
Uncle Zhong.

40
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,280
To think the capital harbors such a

41
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,340
well-trained assassination squad.

42
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,040
It's knockout smoke.

43
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,760
Li Yunmo.

44
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,530
Uncle Zhong.

45
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,280
The Master is missing.

46
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:19,320
Run!

47
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,440
Father.

48
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,000
You inhaled too much knockout smoke,

49
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,060
so your body hasn't fully recovered.

50
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,100
Sit down first.

51
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,360
How is my father?

52
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,250
There is still no sign of General Xiao.

53
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:50,560
Are you looking for this?

54
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,960
This is from last night.

55
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:57,220
It was torn from the assassin's clothes.

56
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,800
Based on this pattern,

57
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,930
we might find a clue.

58
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,730
Let's stop here.

59
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,320
You won't tell me,

60
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:09,620
which makes me even more certain.

61
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,340
This is the Xuanniao pattern.

62
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,840
It is said that

63
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,800
within the Imperial Guard Office that protects the capital,

64
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,880
there is an assassination squad directly under the Emperor

65
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,600
called the Xuanniao Division.

66
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,800
No one has ever seen it

67
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,480
because everyone who did is dead.

68
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,690
If you hadn't helped me last night,

69
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,800
I'm afraid I'd be dead,

70
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,050
just like my family.

71
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,600
To secure his throne

72
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,520
and weaken the Xiao Family Army,

73
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:42,520
Li Yunxi actually committed such a vicious act.

74
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,080
He is so cruel.

75
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,540
What do you plan to do next?

76
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,240
Find Father first.

77
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,720
If Father isn't there,

78
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:03,360
the 30,000 Xiao Family Army troops stationed in the capital

79
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,680
might cause trouble.

80
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,480
Your Majesty,

81
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,880
spies report that

82
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,760
the Empress is currently at Prince Qi's Manor.

83
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,690
He is awake. It is nothing serious.

84
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,250
Do you know who the assassin is?

85
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,940
Not yet. We are still investigating.

86
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,320
Ah Ling.

87
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,970
Everything is fine in the army.

88
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,260
As for your family,

89
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,280
the Emperor has suppressed the news.

90
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,600
No one knows about it yet.

91
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,800
What about my father?

92
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,850
There is still no news of General Xiao.

93
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,760
But I have sent men

94
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:46,090
to expand the search throughout the city.

95
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,159
Come. Have a drink.

96
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,120
Yunmo.

97
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,080
After all these years,

98
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,480
I am glad you haven't changed.

99
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,409
You are still my brother-in-arms.

100
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:13,140
The Empress is certainly enjoying herself.

101
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,800
Since Your Majesty is here,

102
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,960
why not sit down for a drink and a chat?

103
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,260
Let's catch up.

104
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,680
I did not come here to drink today.

105
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,780
I came to take the Empress back to the palace.

106
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,679
Li Yunxi.

107
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,000
You did everything to keep me in the palace.

108
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,400
What exactly is your purpose?

109
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,840
Your Majesty knows very well

110
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,770
that she is not happy in the palace.

111
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,980
Since he cannot be found outside,

112
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,300
my father is likely in the palace.

113
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,600
I must return.

114
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:08,690
Besides,

115
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,640
I cannot leave Hanxing behind.

116
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,880
If you remain outside,

117
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,600
the 30,000 Xiao Family troops near the capital

118
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,730
will be your shield.

119
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:16,960
But once you return to the palace,

120
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,120
I fear...

121
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,650
You have done enough for me.

122
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,000
When I next leave the palace,

123
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,460
I will come drink with you.

124
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,600
I'll go back with you.

125
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,000
I am not your Empress.

126
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,810
I left you a divorce letter.

127
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,760
What divorce letter?

128
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,560
I didn't see it.

129
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,680
Severing all ties.

130
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,040
Divorce.

131
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,400
Just now, in front of Li Yunmo,

132
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,440
why didn't you say we were divorced?

133
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,100
Or that you aren't my Empress?

134
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,460
Let me tell you.

135
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,040
I'm returning to the palace with you

136
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,370
for the sake of my family

137
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,920
and my father.

138
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,960
As for your family,

139
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,920
I won't tell you anything.

140
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,480
Li Yunxi.

141
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,400
You know full well

142
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:24,240
that killing you is child's play for me.

143
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,360
At worst,

144
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,600
we'll go down together.

145
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,000
Your father

146
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,520
is in the palace dungeon.
